I"∞<h3 id="program-flow">Program Flow</h3>

<p>Below is a flowchart for the main operations for ConFlo.</p>

<p>Each argument is based on the C-W-D model. (Claim-Warrant-Data)
Each argument has one claim and should contain no more than three warrants.</p>

<p>‚ÄúChecks‚Äù are when one player wants to point out the fallacies behind the warrants and request the opposition to refine their arguments. They can also request the other party to clarify the reasoning behind the warrants. A check will make an API call to GPT-3 to confirm whether a logical fallacy has been commited.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/blog2/ConFloChart.png" width="500" /></p>

